 margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .order-guide-list li:last-child {\n            margin-bottom: 0;\n        }\n    }\n<\/style>\n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"TagWrap\">\n    <!-- <h2 title=\"Hair Density Standards\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\" class=\"page-ttl\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/header.jpg\" alt=\"Hair Density Standards\" width=\"1900\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/header.jpg\">\n        <span><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/header_sp.jpg\" alt=\"Hair Density Standards\" width=\"750\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/header_sp.jpg\"><\/span>\n    <\/h2> -->\n    <div class=\"bw-1000 uk-margin-top\">\n        <p>Hair system density refers to the amount of hair that is integrated or ventilated onto the base of a hairpiece. Picking the right density is crucial to ensure that the hair system looks natural and believable on the wearer.<\/p>\n        <p>At LaVivid, we provide a range of 6 density levels that span from \"Extra Light 60%\" to \"Heavy 180%.\".The appropriate density will depend on various factors, such as the wearer's age, natural hair density, and hairstyle preferences.<\/p>\n\n        <h2 class=\"density-guide-ttl\">LAVIVID HAIR DENSITY STANDARDS<\/h2>\n        <p class=\"uk-text-center\">The hair density standard varies among vendors, so our density may not align with that of other vendors.<\/p>\n        <ul class=\"density-list\">\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img01.jpg\" alt=\"Extra Light 60%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img01.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img02.jpg\" alt=\"Light 80%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img02.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img03.jpg\" alt=\"Medium Light 90%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img03.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img04.jpg\" alt=\"Medium Light 100%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img04.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img05.jpg\" alt=\"Medium Light 115%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img05.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img06.jpg\" alt=\"Medium 130%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img06.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img07.jpg\" alt=\"Heavy 150%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img07.jpg\"><\/li>\n            <li><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img08.jpg\" alt=\"Extra Heavy 180%\" width=\"228\" height=\"279\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img08.jpg\"><\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n\n        <h2 class=\"density-guide-ttl\">HOW DOES AGE AFFECT\n            THE CHOICE OF HAIR DENSITY?<\/h2>\n        <div uk-grid=\"\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-2@m uk-width-1-1@s\">\n                <table class=\"guide-table\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n                    <tbody>\n<tr>\n                        <th>Age<\/th>\n                        <th>Density<\/th>\n                        <th>Effect<\/th>\n                    <\/tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>Over 60<\/td>\n                        <td>60%-80%<\/td>\n                        <td>Light density<\/td>\n                    <\/tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>46-60<\/td>\n                        <td>90%-100%<\/td>\n                        <td>Medium Light density<\/td>\n                    <\/tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>25-45<\/td>\n                        <td>115%-120%<\/td>\n                        <td>Medium Light density<\/td>\n                    <\/tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>Up to 25<\/td>\n                        <td>120%-130%<\/td>\n                        <td>Medium Light to Medium density<\/td>\n                    <\/tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>Very few<\/td>\n                        <td>150%-180%<\/td>\n                        <td>Heavy density<\/td>\n                    <\/tr>\n                <\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-2@m uk-width-1-1@s\">\n                <p>There is a general rule that you need to pick a density that is appropriate to your age. If you are in the older range, your hair will be lighter, and you may be in the super light (60%) to light (80%) range. If you're in your 20s and your bio hair is also thick, you may be in the range of medium light to medium range which is around 100% to 130%. If you are in your 30s or even 40s, a more proper density would be around 90% -95%. It's easy to get greedy when we first get the mens hair system and think we want all the hair in the world. But sometimes a more subtle look is better.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <h2 class=\"density-guide-ttl\">HOW DOES HAIR SYSTEM BASE\n            AFFECT THE CHOICE OF DENSITY?<\/h2>\n        <p class=\"uk-text-center\">Different bases carry different amounts of hair.\n            The most delicate ultra thin skin base can only hold a light to medium light density, whereas a mono or a silk base can hold a medium to heavy density hair.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"uk-text-lead uk-text-uppercase uk-text-center uk-margin-medium-top\">BASES AND THE HIGHEST DENSITY THEY CAN CARRY<\/div>\n    <ul class=\"bases-product-list\">\n        <li><a href=\"\/skin-hair-systems\/eros-men-s-hair-system-full-ultra-thin-skin-base-businessmen-s-choice_p43.html\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img09.jpg\" alt=\"TP1802  Eros\" width=\"325\" height=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img09.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n        <li><a href=\"\/skin-hair-systems\/mirage-toupee-for-men-full-super-thin-skin-base-celebrities-choice_p44.html\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img10.jpg\" alt=\"TP1804  Mirage\" width=\"325\" height=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img10.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n        <li><a href=\"\/skin-hair-systems\/achilles-men-s-hair-unit-full-skin-base-men-s-hairstyle-for-thin-hair_p59.html\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img11.jpg\" alt=\"TP1808  Achilles\" width=\"325\" height=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img11.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n        <li><a href=\"\/lace-hair-systems\/helios-hair-system-for-bald-men-full-swiss-lace-base-best-for-active-lifestyle_p45.html\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img12.jpg\" alt=\"TP1805  Helios\" width=\"325\" height=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img12.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n        <li><a href=\"\/mono-hair-systems\/versalite-men-s-hair-pieces-for-wedding-fine-mono-with-pu-cutaways-popular-style_p69.html\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img13.jpg\" alt=\"TP1809  Versalite\" width=\"325\" height=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img13.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <div class=\"bw-1000\">\n        <h2 class=\"density-guide-ttl\">CONSIDER YOUR EXISTING HAIR WHEN\n            YOU PICK A HAIR SYSTEM DENSITY<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"density-guide-box\">\n            <p>For people who are experiencing male pattern baldness, it is quite common to see they have no hair on the top of the head but still have thick hair on the sides. In this case, you can choose a density that will blend in with your existing hair.\n                Send us a few pictures of your existing hair like below to support@lavividhair.com and our experts will assist you pick out a suitable hair system density.<\/p>\n            <img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img14.jpg\" alt=\"TP1802  Eros\" width=\"687\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/density-guide\/img14.jpg\">\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"faq-category-box\">\n            <div class=\"block-title faq-category-heading text-center\">\n                <h2>Hair Density FAQs<\/h2>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <ul uk-accordion=\"multiple: true\" class=\"faq-category-content row\">\n                <li>\n                    <p class=\"name uk-accordion-title\">Which hair density is the best?<\/p>\n                    <div class=\"content uk-accordion-content\">\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"de-de\" xml:lang=\"de-de\">A hair density which is appropriate to your age, blends in with your existing hair, works with your hairstyle, can be called a best density for you. <\/span><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n                <li>\n                    <p class=\"name uk-accordion-title\">Which hair density to choose for a first-time try?<\/p>\n                    <div class=\"content uk-accordion-content\">\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"de-de\" xml:lang=\"de-de\">It's common to struggle with selecting the appropriate hair density and feel uncertain about where to begin. You actually need to actually experience with a few different densities to see which one works for you the best. Starting with a medium light density is generally a safe bet, as it's a popular choice for 90% of people. If you're unsure which density to select, you can always opt for one of our top-selling products: Mirage or Helios. Helios is ideal for those who are highly active or prone to sweating, while Mirage and Helios both make great options if you don't fall into that category.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n                <li>\n                    <p class=\"name uk-accordion-title\">Is it possible to have different densities across different parts of the hair unit?<\/p>\n                    <div class=\"content uk-accordion-content\">\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"de-de\" xml:lang=\"de-de\">Yes, not a problem. We can make this happen with a custom order.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <h2 class=\"density-guide-ttl\">CHECK OTHER HAIR SYSTEM ORDERING GUIDES<\/h2>\n        <ul class=\"order-guide-list\">\n            <li><a href=\"\/content\/hair-system-base-guide-52\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner05.jpg\" alt=\"Hair System Base Guide\" width=\"580\" height=\"109\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner05.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n            <li><a href=\"\/content\/hair-system-color-guide-50\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner04.jpg\" alt=\"Hair System Color Chart\" width=\"580\" height=\"109\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner04.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n            <li><a href=\"\/content\/front-contour-shapes-guide-54\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner02.jpg\" alt=\"Front Contour Shapes Guide\" width=\"580\" height=\"109\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner02.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n            <li><a href=\"\/content\/hair-system-wave-or-curl-guide-51\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner01.jpg\" alt=\"Hair System Curl Wave Guide\" width=\"580\" height=\"109\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/order-guide\/banner01.jpg\"><\/a><\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>"}}},"block_order":["html_jaUkPV"],"name":"自定义 HTML 内容","settings":{"section_title":"","title_size":32,"title_color":"#000000","title_alignment":"center","title_margin":40,"container_type":"full-width","container_width":1180,"container_padding":15,"background_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"use_shadow_dom":true,"custom_css":"","custom_js":""}}},"order":["main","common_banner_eQhYBw","custom_html_content_qfNp6P"]}